===============================================================================

CHANGELOG:

v0.5:
- add /fight dice command for choosing iron sword or bow
- add /fight next command to display details of the next fight
- add /fight next <message> command to set the details of the next fight
- add /fight next clear command to delete the message
- add a configuration file. on default you have to use permissions and are able
	to set up a countdown as long as you want

v0.4:
- fix issue #6, the countdown no longer blocks the chat 
	and several other things
- add a help and an info page, use '/fight help' for more information
- the countdown is now visible in the server console

v0.3:
- add announcement befor the countdown starts
- add compatibility with Permissions

v0.2:
- change /fight to /fight <seconds>

v0.1:
- add /fight to count from 5 to 1


===============================================================================

DEPENDENCIES:

- Bukkit (http://www.bukkit.org) - A SMP plugin API
- Permissions (http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/5974/)
	- An permission system for Bukkit


===============================================================================

PERMISSIONS:

- fightcountdown.dice
	for /fight dice
- fightcountdown.next
	for /fight next <message>
- fightcountdown.next.clear
	for /fight next clear
- fightcountdown.set
	for /fight set <seconds>

===============================================================================

COMMANDS:

/fight help - a help little help page
/fight info - an info about this plugin
/fight dice - chooses between iron sword and bow
/fight next - gives you the details of the next fight
/fight next <message> - sets the details of the next fight
/fight next clear - to delete the message
/fight set <seconds> - set up a countdown.
	fightcountdown.fight (to allow the '/fight set' command in Permissions)